On launch you will see loading and then after a minute or so you will see:

Decompressed: filmies.tsv.gz
Decompressed: raties.tsv.gz

Once decompressed it will give you, your first film with the option to play or pass.

To play hit 'Y' or type 'Play' then enter and you will see the film highlight green. 
To pass simply hit enter to be provided with another film.
If it has presented you with a film you have already done or wish to never do hit 'd' or type 'done' to add it to list of precompleted movies.

Once playing you will have the option to hit 'a' or 'results' or 'r' to see all the answers come up in blue font.

Once you have revealed the answers hitting enter again will exit the application.
